#Title: Sum of n + nn + nnn
#Date: 10/6/2015
#Purpose:  This program takes a number n, and calculates the sum of n + nn + nnn.
For example, the user inputs the number 6.  The program calculates the sum of 6 + 66 + 666 = 738.

n = int(raw_input("Enter a positive integer: "))
nn = 10*n + n
nnn = 100*n + nn
add = n + nn + nnn
print "The sum of n + nn + nnn is: " + str(add)
